Package: hiddenmeta
Type: Package
Title: Meta-analysis of hidden population studies
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2020-11-12
Author: 
    c(person("Georgiy", "Syunyaev", email = "gs2716@columbia.edu",
             role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Macartan", "Humphreys", email = "macartan@gmail.com",
             role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Georgiy Syunyaev <gs2716@columbia.edu>
Description: This package provides helper functions for RDS, TLS and proportional sampling 
    from hidden populations. The functions allow for easy declaration of one or more studies
    with various design features. In addition, package provides functions for meta-analysis of
    performance comparison of various estimation methods based on RDS and proportional sampling.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    magrittr,
    tidyr,
    DeclareDesign,
    RcppAlgos,
    pbapply,
    parallel
